    <section_number>111</section_number>
    <catch_line>Beneficiary; Power To Sue   </catch_line>
    <order_by>111</order_by>
    <text>
        The beneficiary under a policy of insurance against loss or damage from disease or by the bodily injury or death by accident of the insured may maintain an action thereon in his own name.
    </text>
